      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Discover your next reliable ride with this fantastic vehicle in good condition! It has been well-maintained and offers a smooth, dependable driving experience that\u2019s perfect for any lifestyle. While it shows a few minor signs of careful previous use, it looks great and is ready to hit the road with its next owner today!",
