      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber. This specimen remains in showroom condition, exhibiting an uncompromising level of care and preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of excellence rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Mechanically sound and aesthetically superior, this vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
