      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising showroom standard. This specimen exhibits a flawless exterior finish complemented by an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every aspect of this automobile reflects meticulous stewardship and a commitment to preservation. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a machine in pristine, investment-grade condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
